column1: Lysander...\| their numbers are far too much for us to survive...

column1: We worked too hard taking over Eastwall to lose it now.\! There is always a way.
column2: Hemos trabajado demasiado para conquistar Muroriente, no podemos perderlo ahora.\! Siempre hay una manera.
